The RHEL-8 auxiliary key uses SHA-1 in its signature. To enable RHEL-8
cross-builds on RHEL-10, we can't include the RHEL-8 auxiliary key in
the repo definitions.

Signed-off-by: Tom Hozza <thozza@redhat.com>
